{"tid":1311379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布拉格真連儂牆被噴上「香港加油」","createTime":"2019-07-13T07:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T11:27:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b73750eaf06768f46cd16f4f852e112a51d20fd","tid":1311379,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190712/_2019071209275481795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190712%2F_2019071209275481795.jpg&h=3778d3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》爭議持續，各區陸續出現連儂牆，讓市民表達意見。位於捷克布拉格的真連儂牆，近日被噴上「香港加油」的字句，旁邊是一名黃衣人的塗鴉，引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆原址位於捷克布拉格，因1988年群眾不滿胡薩克共產主義政權，在布拉格修道院大廣場的一面牆寫上反抗標語，當中包括傳奇樂隊Beatles的靈魂人物John Lennon的肖像及歌詞，因為John Lennon自80年代起，被視為反戰、追求和平的重要文化象徵符號。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的，是John Lennon在1980年12月8日於紐約公寓遭瘋狂歌迷槍殺，故他沒有到過連儂牆，但群眾將他的精神以塗鴉、文字，甚至街頭演唱的形式延續下去。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆有一個不明文規定，就是有顏料在手，就可以不必管前者的塗鴉畫上創作，所以連儂牆的模樣不停在轉變，唯一不變的就是和平、反戰的信息一直都在。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1542631/即時-港聞-Kelly-Online-布拉格真連儂牆被噴上-香港加油-同John-Lennon有咩關係</code></pre>"},{"pid":"76e6f79e3227036d36ec6ad14b41dda1643b3776","tid":1311379,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"顏料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係memo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc97e1509ddee8871de8d2bb47fdf9f6d429edde","tid":1311379,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"超勁<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"740a0323381006d3d89ffdaf4c2c7cad60194c66","tid":1311379,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff18a42e62dca284b4806dad2470008e6c31e12e","tid":1311379,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"邊位絲"},{"pid":"fd6470ded9649006d4f850a0ed8c37e91229db49","tid":1311379,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}